metadata.description: A vibrant tribute to the emergence of our new era, this digital artwork celebrates the aesthetics of Vaporwave with a bold and colorful palette. Drawing upon the colorful neon lights of Cyberpunk and the drippy ease of Synthwave, it offers a unique fusion of distinct styles that come together to delight us. The photography, the art, the music and the glitch work creates a seamless blend of all aesthetics, painting the viewer with neon in a color palette is as bold and colorful as the 80s themselves.
metadata.name: VaporBreak
